Package com.maxwellwheeler.plugins.tppets.commands

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CommandLost
    Object that processes /tpp lost commands
    CommandPermissions
    Object that processes tpp pet permission commands: /tpp allow [username] [pet name] /tpp remove [username] [pet name] /tpp list [pet name]
    CommandProtected
    Object that processes /tpp protected commands.
    CommandRename
    Object that processes tpp pet rename commands: /tpp rename [existing pet name] [new pet name] /tpp rename f:[username] [existing pet name] [new pet name]
    CommandTPP
    Core command handler to the plugin.
    CommandTPPets
    Processes commands that actually teleport pets around
    RegionCommand
    Template for CommandProtected and {CommandLost
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    CommandPermissions.EditResult
    Enum representing results of a /tpp allow or /tpp remove, so that specific feedback can be given to the player.
